    <title>Learning of Markdowm</title>
    <url>/2020/05/22/Markdown%20getting%20Start/</url>
    <content><![CDATA[<h3 id="What-is-MarkDown"><a href="#What-is-MarkDown" class="headerlink" title="What is MarkDown"></a>What is MarkDown</h3><p>Markdown is a lightweight “markup language”. The founder is John Gruber, which replaces typesetting with concise grammar. It is recently widely used by more and more knowledge works, writing enthusiasts, programmers or researchers. There are no more than ten commonly used markup symbols. Compared to the more complex HTML markup language, Markdown is very lightweight, and the learning cost does not need too much.</p>
<a id="more"></a>

<h3 id="The-common-grammars-of-Markdown"><a href="#The-common-grammars-of-Markdown" class="headerlink" title="The common grammars of Markdown"></a>The common grammars of Markdown</h3><h4 id="Setting-Headings"><a href="#Setting-Headings" class="headerlink" title="Setting Headings"></a>Setting Headings</h4><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs bash"><span class="hljs-comment"># the level 1 Heading</span><br><span class="hljs-comment">## the level 2 Heading</span><br><span class="hljs-comment">### the level 3 Heading</span><br><span class="hljs-comment">#### the level 4 Heading</span><br><span class="hljs-comment">##### the level 5 Heading</span><br><span class="hljs-comment">##### the level 6 Heading</span><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<h4 id="Blod-text"><a href="#Blod-text" class="headerlink" title="Blod text"></a>Blod text</h4><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs bash">**Bloding text**<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<p><strong>Bloding text</strong></p>
<h4 id="Italic"><a href="#Italic" class="headerlink" title="Italic"></a>Italic</h4><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs bash">*Italic*<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<p><em>Italic</em></p>
<h4 id="Underline"><a href="#Underline" class="headerlink" title="Underline"></a>Underline</h4><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs bash">&lt;u&gt;Underline&lt;/u&gt;<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<p><u>Underline</u></p>
<h4 id="Strikethough"><a href="#Strikethough" class="headerlink" title="Strikethough"></a>Strikethough</h4><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs bash">~~Strikthough~~<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<p><del>Strikethough</del></p>
<h4 id="Adding-Divider"><a href="#Adding-Divider" class="headerlink" title="Adding Divider"></a>Adding Divider</h4><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs bash">Adding Divider<br>***<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<p>Adding Divider</p>
<hr>
<h4 id="Quoted-text"><a href="#Quoted-text" class="headerlink" title="Quoted text"></a>Quoted text</h4><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs bash">&gt;Quoted text<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<blockquote>
<p>Quoted text</p>
</blockquote>
<h4 id="Add-symbol-list-or-number-list"><a href="#Add-symbol-list-or-number-list" class="headerlink" title="Add symbol list or number list"></a>Add symbol list or number list</h4><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs bash">* Add<br>* symbol<br>* list<br><br>1. or<br>2. number<br>3. list<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<ul>
<li>Add</li>
<li>symbol</li>
<li>list</li>
</ul>
<ol>
<li>or</li>
<li>number</li>
<li>list</li>
</ol>
<h4 id="Add-a-to-do-list"><a href="#Add-a-to-do-list" class="headerlink" title="Add a to-do list"></a>Add a to-do list</h4><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs bash">* [x] Add<br>* [ ] a to-do list<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<ul>
<li><input checked="" disabled="" type="checkbox"> Add</li>
<li><input disabled="" type="checkbox"> a to-do list</li>
</ul>
<h4 id="Insert-link"><a href="#Insert-link" class="headerlink" title="Insert link"></a>Insert link</h4><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs bash">[Fzz<span class="hljs-string">'s Blog](https://fzzcode.github.io/)</span><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<p><a href="https://fzzcode.github.io" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Fzz’s Blog</a></p>
<h4 id="Insert-image"><a href="#Insert-image" class="headerlink" title="Insert image"></a>Insert image</h4><h5 id="the-internet-image"><a href="#the-internet-image" class="headerlink" title="the internet image"></a>the internet image</h5><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs bash">![image](https://www.yinxiang.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/%E5%94%AE%E7%A5%A8%E5%BE%AE%E4%BF%A1%E5%B0%81%E9%9D%A22.png)<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<p><img src="https://www.yinxiang.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/%E5%94%AE%E7%A5%A8%E5%BE%AE%E4%BF%A1%E5%B0%81%E9%9D%A22.png" alt="image"></p>
<h5 id="the-local-image"><a href="#the-local-image" class="headerlink" title="the local image"></a>the local image</h5><p>you can control the size of local images bu the belowing grammars.</p>
<ul>
<li>@w=300</li>
<li>@h=150</li>
<li>@w=200h=100</li>
<li>@h=100w=200</li>
</ul>
<figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs bash">0feea425bebb33aa45691b125b74d55b.png@w=300<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<p><img src="en-resource://database/936:1" alt="0feea425bebb33aa45691b125b74d55b.png">@w=300</p>
<h4 id="Insert-form"><a href="#Insert-form" class="headerlink" title="Insert form"></a>Insert form</h4><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs bash">|A|B|C|D|<br>|---|---|---|---|<br>|1000|100|10|1|<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<table>
<thead>
<tr>
<th>A</th>
<th>B</th>
<th>C</th>
<th>D</th>
</tr>
</thead>
<tbody><tr>
<td>1000</td>
<td>100</td>
<td>10</td>
<td>1</td>
</tr>
</tbody></table>
<h4 id="Insert-inline-code-or-code-block"><a href="#Insert-inline-code-or-code-block" class="headerlink" title="Insert inline code or code block"></a>Insert inline code or code block</h4><p>the example is the highlight of Python.</p>
<h5 id="Insert-inline-code"><a href="#Insert-inline-code" class="headerlink" title="Insert inline code"></a>Insert inline code</h5><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs bash">Insert inline ``pyhon <span class="hljs-built_in">print</span>(<span class="hljs-string">"hello world!"</span>)<br>``code<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<p>Insert inline <code>pyhon print(&quot;hello world!&quot;)</code>code</p>
<h5 id="Insert-code-block"><a href="#Insert-code-block" class="headerlink" title="Insert code block"></a>Insert code block</h5><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs python"><span class="hljs-comment">#!/usr/bin/python</span><br><span class="hljs-keyword">import</span> re<br><br>line = <span class="hljs-string">"Cats are smarter than dogs"</span><br>matchObj = re.match( <span class="hljs-string">r'(.*) are (.*?) .*'</span>, line, re.M|re.I)<br><span class="hljs-keyword">if</span> matchObj:<br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">print</span> <span class="hljs-string">"matchObj.group() : "</span>, matchObj.group()<br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">print</span> <span class="hljs-string">"matchObj.group(1) : "</span>, matchObj.group(<span class="hljs-number">1</span>)<br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">print</span> <span class="hljs-string">"matchObj.group(2) : "</span>, matchObj.group(<span class="hljs-number">2</span>)<br><span class="hljs-keyword">else</span>:<br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">print</span> <span class="hljs-string">"No match!!"</span><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<h4 id="Insert-Math-formula"><a href="#Insert-Math-formula" class="headerlink" title="Insert Math formula"></a>Insert Math formula</h4><p>Markdown supports almost LaTeX math formulas</p>
<p>inline: $e^{i\pi}+1=0$<br>outline:<br>$$e^{i\pi}+1=0$$</p>
<p>for more math formulas you can refer to:<br><a href="https://khan.github.io/KaTeX/docs/supported.html" target="_blank" rel="noopener">https://khan.github.io/KaTeX/docs/supported.html</a></p>
<h4 id="Insert-flow-chart"><a href="#Insert-flow-chart" class="headerlink" title="Insert flow chart"></a>Insert flow chart</h4><pre class="mermaid">graph TD
A[module A] -->|A1|B(module B)
B -->C{condition C}
C -->|condition C1|D[module D]
C -->|condition C2|E(module E)
C -->|condition C3|F{condition G}</pre>
<h4 id="Insert-sequence-Diagram"><a href="#Insert-sequence-Diagram" class="headerlink" title="Insert sequence Diagram"></a>Insert sequence Diagram</h4><pre class="mermaid">sequenceDiagram 
A->B: Connect test 
A->>B: Have you recieved the message? 
B-->>A: Recieved message</pre>
<h4 id="Insert-Gantt-chart"><a href="#Insert-Gantt-chart" class="headerlink" title="Insert Gantt chart"></a>Insert Gantt chart</h4><pre class="mermaid">gantt
title Gantt Chart
dateFormat YYY-MM-DD
section ProjectA
task1 :2020-05-23, 4d
task2 :after task1,3d
section ProjectB
task3 :2020-05-24, 5d
task4 :10d</pre>

<h3 id="Reference"><a href="#Reference" class="headerlink" title="Reference"></a>Reference</h3><p>this flog is translated from <a href="https://list.yinxiang.com/markdown/eef42447-db3f-48ee-827b-1bb34c03eb83.php" target="_blank" rel="noopener">印象笔记 Markdown 入门指南</a>, you can click this link for details.</p>
]]></content>
